<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV41">
<l>āyaṉāki yāyarmaṅkai vēyatōḷvi rumpiṉāy</l>
<l>āyaniṉṉai yāvarvalla ramparatto ṭimparāy</l>
<l>māya.māya māyaikol lataṉṟinīva kuttalum</l>
<l>māyamāya mākkiṉāyuṉ māyamuṟṟu māyamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Turning into a cowherd, You desired the bamboo[-like] shoulders of the cowherdess!</l>
<l>Who [among] the celestials and people of this world can search You?</l>
<l>O wonderful [Lord]! Is th[at] wonder an illusion?  Apart from that,</l>
<l>[despite] Your creation, You did the wonder [of ensuring that the creatures] died.</l>
<l rend="indent">Your wonder is wholly wonderful!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
